{"word":"ξύλον","slug":"ξύλον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ξύλον, ου, τό</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ IE\">IE</a>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘product of a fibrous plant’, <b>wood<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in general, as material <b><a href='B:530 3:12'>1 Cor 3:12</a>; <a href='B:730 18:12'>Rv 18:12</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> by <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> of things made of wood <b>club/cudgel <a href='B:470 26:47'>Mt 26:47</a>; stocks <a href='B:510 16:24'>Ac 16:24</a>; cross <a href='B:510 5:30'>5:30</a>; <a href='B:510 10:39'>10:39</a>; <a href='B:550 3:13'>Gal 3:13</a>; <a href='B:670 2:24'>1 Pt 2:24</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘sturdy fibrous plant as such’, <b>tree <a href='B:490 23:31'>Lk 23:31</a>; <a href='B:730 2:7'>Rv 2:7</a>; <a href='B:730 22:2'>22:2</a>, <a href='B:730 22:14'>14</a>, <a href='B:730 22:19'>19</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ξύλινος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ξυν-\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}